13
00:02:21,580 --> 00:02:22,180
As long as I'm sure

14
00:02:22,180 --> 00:02:23,660
you have a place to stay in Luoshan

15
00:02:24,140 --> 00:02:24,540
and you're safe,

16
00:02:25,140 --> 00:02:25,820
I'll leave.

17
00:02:27,100 --> 00:02:27,940
After all, we are both

18
00:02:28,020 --> 00:02:29,100
from Kangjiadong, Lureed Village.

19
00:02:30,260 --> 00:02:31,300
(So this stickybeak)

20
00:02:31,420 --> 00:02:32,300
(is a fellow villager)

21
00:02:32,380 --> 00:02:33,340
(of the real Jiang Xiaoyuan.)

22
00:02:33,820 --> 00:02:35,140
