24
00:02:37,900 --> 00:02:38,340
(This won't do.)

25
00:02:38,980 --> 00:02:40,060
(I have to get rid of him quickly.)

26
00:04:51,780 --> 00:04:55,180
[Ladies' Room]

27
00:05:28,700 --> 00:05:29,100
Excuse me,

28
00:05:30,100 --> 00:05:31,020
