29
00:05:31,780 --> 00:05:32,940
Could you please help me check on her?

30
00:05:34,380 --> 00:05:35,620
There should be no one inside.

31
00:05:36,100 --> 00:05:37,020
But a girl just jumped

32
00:05:37,060 --> 00:05:37,900
out of the window.

33
00:06:25,860 --> 00:06:26,660
Young lady, may I help you?

34
