[Fried egg 2 yuan, Rice 3 yuan]

35
00:07:06,460 --> 00:07:06,940
Madam,

36
00:07:07,460 --> 00:07:08,660
could you clear this table?

37
00:07:09,300 --> 00:07:10,220
Sure, just a moment.

38
00:07:10,740 --> 00:07:11,700
You may order first.

39
00:07:13,660 --> 00:07:15,180
I'll have two-thirds of a bowl of rice.

40
00:07:18,780 --> 00:07:19,180
What?

41
00:07:20,940 --> 00:07:21,540
You only want

42
00:07:21,540 --> 00:07:22,780
two-thirds?

43
00:07:23,340 --> 00:07:25,220
Just rice without a dish?

44
00:07:27,740 --> 00:07:28,460
What a weirdo.

45
00:07:33,060 --> 00:07:34,180
Take a seat, wait here.

46
00:07:46,580 --> 00:07:47,460
That old phone

47
00:07:47,580 --> 00:07:49,260
